data.description: Rare BEAUTY in the NW for under $400k!!! Walk up your private culd-e-sac through the front door to this beautifully updated 2 story home. Downstairs you will find a complete open floorplan with gorgeous vaulted ceilings where you can enjoy friends & family all throughout, updated with trendy wood-like laminate flooring, grey paint with accents of blue, right into your dining and kitchen. The open kitchen boasts black & stainless steel appliances, grey cabinetry, large pantry, and plenty of counter space to cook and entertain! Walk upstairs to your double door primary bedroom with en suite and walk closet, accompanied by two additional bedrooms with a full bath. Definitely do not forget to check out that BACKYARD! REAL GRASS, plenty of space to entertain, complete with an elevated deck and fire pit. You do not want to wait on this one~ come take a look, it won't last long!!
